App Design is like Apple app
### Use iOS Design Principles like
- **Spring Physics**: Natural, bouncy animations yang terasa like native iOS
- **Press Feedback**: Scale-down effect saat element di-tap (0.97 scale)
- **Glass Effect**: Frosted glass navbar dan footer dengan backdrop blur
- **Haptic Feedback**: Vibration API untuk tactile response
- **Staggered Animations**: Sequential entrance animations untuk lists
- **Gesture Recognition**: Swipe-to-delete, pull-to-refresh, drag-to-dismiss
